  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      277.63,
      110.11,
      337.4,
      123.39
    ],
    "text": "Judgement",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      147.86,
      143.3,
      161.14
    ],
    "text": "Introduction",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      185.39,
      543.15,
      198.67
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner is a mother of a minor named P.M.A.Omindu Hansaja Premarathna, and the said",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      213.14,
      543.09,
      226.42
    ],
    "text": "minor had received a Deed of Gift bearing No. 5494/013, dated 13.10.2023 and attested by Kushan",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      240.64,
      543.21,
      253.92
    ],
    "text": "Hettiarachchi Notary Public; the protocol of the Deed of Gift is annexed to the Petition as P1. The",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      268.16,
      542.68,
      281.44
    ],
    "text": "said Notary had sent it for registration to the Land Registrar of Kandy. However, the Land",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      295.91,
      543.17,
      309.19
    ],
    "text": "Registrar had first registered it and later cancelled the registration; therefore, later, he refused to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      323.41,
      197.58,
      336.69
    ],
    "text": "register the original deed.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      361.18,
      542.66,
      374.46
    ],
    "text": "Thereafter, the Petitioner has appealed to the Registrar General, who had refused the said appeal",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      388.68,
      543.17,
      401.96
    ],
    "text": "and notified the same to the Land Registrar of Kandy with a copy of the Attorney-at-Law through",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      416.18,
      543.13,
      429.46
    ],
    "text": "whom the Petitioner had made the appeal. The refusal of the said appeal is that there is a pending",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      443.96,
      542.64,
      457.24
    ],
    "text": "case before the Kandy Magistrate\u2019s Court, which inquires into the allegations of fraud in the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      471.46,
      214.35,
      484.74
    ],
    "text": "preparation of the said deed.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      508.98,
      542.63,
      522.26
    ],
    "text": "Subsequently, having notified the Registrar General and the Land Registrar of Kandy, the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      536.73,
      543.17,
      550.01
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner seeks to invoke the writ jurisdiction of this Court to quash the decision of the Land",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      564.23,
      542.87,
      577.51
    ],
    "text": "Registrar of Kandy refusing to return the said original deed, and also compelling the Respondents",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      592.01,
      372.4,
      605.29
    ],
    "text": "to return the same to the Notary through a Writ of Mandamus.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      629.51,
      542.89,
      642.79
    ],
    "text": "This has been supported on 07.08.2025, and after issuance of formal notice on support, the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      657.01,
      321.63,
      670.29
    ],
    "text": "Respondents have filed their respective Objections.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      724.78,
      312.13,
      754.09
    ],
    "text": "4",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      72.59,
      542.82,
      85.87
    ],
    "text": "According to their Objections, they have admitted that they did not return the said deed because it",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      100.09,
      543.2,
      113.37
    ],
    "text": "was handed over to the Special Crime Investigation Division (SCID) of Kandy, to investigate the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      127.86,
      542.76,
      141.14
    ],
    "text": "allegations of fraud. In addition to that, since there is such an allegation against the perpetrators,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      155.36,
      424.43,
      168.64
    ],
    "text": "they are unable to register the same and return the original to the Notary.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      193.14,
      542.99,
      206.42
    ],
    "text": "Thereafter, this was argued before me on 27.11.2025, and in addition to the oral arguments, the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      220.64,
      454.95,
      233.92
    ],
    "text": "Written Submissions were filed, elaborating their respective arguments further.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      258.13,
      135.3,
      271.41
    ],
    "text": "Arguments",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      295.91,
      542.8,
      309.19
    ],
    "text": "It is the Petitioner\u2019s contention that the refusal to return the original deed for registration is illegal",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      322.47,
      542.76,
      336.69
    ],
    "text": "since the 2nd Respondent has refused to register the same without any proper cause or reason.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      351.18,
      196.08,
      364.46
    ],
    "text": "Therefore, it is irrational.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      388.68,
      542.69,
      401.96
    ],
    "text": "The thrust of the argument made by Mr. Amarajeewa is that the Registrar cannot simply reject the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      416.18,
      542.92,
      429.46
    ],
    "text": "registration of a document submitted for registration to the Registrar of Lands merely on suspicion",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      443.96,
      543.06,
      457.24
    ],
    "text": "that the recipient (donee), a minor, has not accepted the donation by placing his signature; whereas,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      471.46,
      542.58,
      484.74
    ],
    "text": "in fact, the guardian has accepted the donation by placing her signature. Therefore, in view of",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      498.96,
      542.65,
      512.24
    ],
    "text": "Section 38 of the Registration of Documents Ordinance, No. 23 of 1927 (as amended), read with",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      526.73,
      542.8,
